keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap J
unmap K
unmap H
unmap L
map J   scrollDown count=5
map K  scrollUp count=5
map H  scrollLeft count=5
map L scrollRight count=5
unmap <C-h>
map <C-h> previousTab
map <C-l> nextTab

unmap x
unmap X
map c removeTab
map C restoreTab



# go to tab
unmap g0
map ø1 firstTab
map ø2 firstTab count=2
map ø3 firstTab count=3 
map ø4 firstTab count=4 
map ø5 firstTab count=5 
map ø6 firstTab count=6 
map ø7 firstTab count=7 
map ø8 firstTab count=8
map ø9 firstTab count=9
map ø0 firstTab count=10 



# clutter
unmap d 
unmap u
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
